title: Ethereum-based Altcoin’s Price Skyrockets 40% in a Day After Upbit Wallet Accumulates 3.3% of Supply
description: The price of an Ethereum-based altcoin, Bancor ($BNT) has recently seen a surge of over 40% in a 24-hour period amid what appeared to be accumulation that has been redirected to a wallet belonging to South Korean cryptocurrency exchange Upbit. According to on-chain monitoring service Lookonchain, the native token of the automated market maker (AMM) […]
